abstract: >-
  OpenEvalGate is a local, deterministic release-assurance framework for
  production AI assistants and agents. Its stable V1 core validates versioned
  evidence, hard blockers, and bounded launch-readiness recommendations.
keywords:
  - generative AI
  - AI governance
  - AI agents
  - LLM evaluation
  - launch readiness
  - human escalation
  - trust preservation
